OL,4,Cfood while at the wheel on motorway
OL,6,FA van driver was caught texting and a
OL,7,Florry driver was spotted eating a jar
OL,8,Fof food while at the wheel during
OL,9,Fpolice patrols on the M5.
OL,11,FOfficers from Gloucestershire Police
OL,12,Fdrove an unmarked HGV to catch
OL,13,Fmotorists committing offences on the
OL,14,Fmotorway from 1 to 4 October.
OL,16,F20 drivers were stopped during the
OL,17,Fcrackdown named Operation Tramline,
OL,18,Fwhich is designed to reduce the number
OL,19,Fof incidents caused by unsafe
OL,20,Fbehaviour on the roads.
