OL,6,FDrivers were stopped for offences
OL,7,Fincluding the use of a mobile phone,
OL,8,Fnot being in proper control of a
OL,9,Fvehicle, failure to wear seatbelts and
OL,10,Fdriving with an insecure load.
OL,12,FOfficers who identified a driver
OL,13,Fcommitting an offence recorded video
OL,14,Ffootage from the unmarked lorry cab
OL,15,Fbefore notifying officers in an
OL,16,Faccompanying car. These officers then
OL,17,Fintercepted the offending vehicle,
OL,18,Fpulling it over and dealing with the
OL,19,Fdriver.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
