OL,6,FSergeant Matt Firth from the Roads
OL,7,FPolicing Unit said: "The use of the
OL,8,FHGV from National Highways enables our
OL,9,FRoads Policing officers to detect some
OL,10,Foffences that would otherwise be a
OL,11,Fchallenge to identify.
OL,13,F"Reducing the numbers of those killed
OL,14,For seriously injured on our roads is a
OL,15,Fpriority for Gloucestershire
OL,16,FConstabulary, and making the roads
OL,17,Fsafer for all is what our communities
OL,18,Fwant our team to be leading on.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
