OL,3,CLorry driver caught eating from jar of
OL,4,Cfood while at the wheel on motorway
OL,6,F"We will continue to deal with
OL,7,Foffences positively, remembering that
OL,8,Fany of us or our loved ones could be
OL,9,Fimpacted by such behaviours whilst
OL,10,Fusing the roads."
OL,12,FNational Highways has three unmarked
OL,13,FHGV cabs which it loans out to police
OL,14,Fforces across the country as part of
OL,15,FOperation Tramline.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
