OL,6,FNational Highways Assistant Regional
OL,7,FSafety Programme Manager Beverley
OL,8,FHannah, said: "Working closely with
OL,9,Four police partners, National Highways
OL,10,Fis striving to stamp out inappropriate
OL,11,Fdriving behaviours on our roads.
OL,13,F"While we always hope that when our
OL,14,FHGVs go out no instances of unsafe
OL,15,Fdriving will be seen, thanks to the
OL,16,Felevated position in the cabs the
OL,17,Fofficers have a clear view into all
OL,18,Fvehicles so those who do put
OL,19,Fthemselves and others at risk can be
OL,20,Fspotted and stopped.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
